111
00:09:46,990 --> 00:09:50,390
Eh, tadi saya tengok leher awak panjang macam zirafah.

112
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,100
Jumpa apa-apa tak?

113
00:09:53,410 --> 00:09:55,930
