172
00:14:40,450 --> 00:14:41,650
Dia sangat hebatlah.

173
00:14:42,130 --> 00:14:44,240
Saya rasa tak ada harapanlah.

174
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,440
Dia jauh lebih kacak daripada awak.

175
