204
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:46,030
Awak kena siasat betul-betul.

205
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:48,330
Detektif Duang.

206
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,380
Pergi.

207
00:17:53,570 --> 00:17:54,280
Pergi.

208
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:58,340
