209
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:00,090
Boleh.

210
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:02,270
Awak tengoklah baik-baik.

211
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:04,360
Saya kan detektif terkenal.

212
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,460
