224
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:57,630
Aduh, kalian berdua ni tak berguna langsung.\nBiar saya pergi sendiri.

225
00:19:35,010 --> 00:19:35,740
[Semua kejayaan berpunca daripada diri sendiri.]

226
00:19:35,410 --> 00:19:36,630
Hei, Duang.

227
00:19:37,370 --> 00:19:38,370
Di sini.

228
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:40,530
Macam mana? Jumpa apa-apa tak?

